texts.text: If you think an e-mail account has been hacked in Plesk, use this to hunt down which one it could be:

texts.label: code
texts.orig: cat /var/log/messages | grep -i smtp_auth | grep "logged in" | awk {' print $11 '} | awk -F / {' print $6"@"$5 '} | sort | uniq -c | sort -n | tail
